song.title: Flight to Austria
song.info:
Music from the invitro to PixelShow 2007 Greek demoparty.
"PixelShow will take place between 11 and 13 of May, 2007 at the theater of Patra's University campus.It's the same place as for the last PixelShow 2005 and exactly in the same spot where ReAct and Gardening 96/97 took place in the past.
We have decided to make a major change to the demo compo. For PixelShow 2007 we will hold a Combined Demo Compo, hopefully, featuring demos on a vast variety of platforms."
